# ThreadSanitizer suppressions for the OpenMP test configuration.
#
# Ubuntu's libomp is not built with TSan instrumentation, so TSan cannot see
# the runtime's internal synchronization and reports false races between
# libomp-internal mutex operations. This suppresses reports whose racing
# access originates inside libomp; races in the (instrumented) library and
# test code still report normally with their own frames.
called_from_lib:libomp.so
